<!--[endif]--><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="text-indent: 5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Bucheon
= Reporter Seok-Cheol Jeong<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span lang="EN-US" style="  serif;   color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">Source: Gyeonggi Daily (</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.kgmaeil.net/"><span style="  serif;   color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">http://www.kgmaeil.net</span></a></span><span lang="EN-US" style="  serif;   color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 2;"><span lang="EN-US" style="  serif;   color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">(Original article) </span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.kgmaeil.net/news/articleView.html?idxno=251030"><span style="  serif;   color: rgb(0, 117, 200);">http://www.kgmaeil.net/news/articleView.html?idxno=251030</span></a></span><span lang="EN-US" style=" "><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="line-height: 2;">&nbsp;</p>


